description: VOLUME UP!!🔊 Have you ever heard the sound of a Southern Cassowary? Our resident cassowaries often get compared to dinosaurs, judging by the size of her cask- who can guess how old “Bertha” really is? #cassowary#zoo#georgiauntamedzoo#dinosaur#hogansvillega#animalsoftiktok🐾 #adventure
